settings.content: This item is great and a very comfortable article of clothing. I got it large so that I could wear it layered over other warm gear. The slippery quilted lining makes it easy to put on over any other type of clothing without binding.

settings.content: Bought this coat for my fiancé after realizing his old coat was 10 years old and small enough to fit me. He doesn’t usually wear a jacket out, but with the cold weather coming on, I wanted something to cover his arms when it snowed.
